# This Vercel project builds the React dashboard in automation-hub-dashboard/
# (see vercel.json). The patterns below are ANCHORED with a leading slash so
# they only match the Python engine / FastAPI hub at the repo ROOT and never
# collide with the dashboard's own folders (e.g. src/data, src/components).
/bot/
/automation-hub/
/api/
/configs/
/data/
/examples/
/tests/
/.github/
/.pytest_cache/
/report.html
/requirements.txt
/pyproject.toml
__pycache__/
*.egg-info/
